d losing data in case that the system would shut down in the middle of
 a work session! " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" 
{TEXT -1 104 "In the text mode (click on the cap T button) place your \+
